          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">fantasy scifi lovers and moms who want an adventure and teens and adults should love it too</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/693356-magma?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
