        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1616359146" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13520207003597281234">This second book in the series returns to the alternate world that Susan visited in the first book. In this one, we follow the new Restorer - the unlikely hero, Kieran - as he struggles to come to terms with the One&apos;s call on his life. We also watch Susan&apos;s teenage son grow and mature in the strange new world.<br/><br/>Again, this story is told beautifully, and the characters are easy to relate to. Another really great read!</span>
  <span id="freeText13520207003597281234" style="display:none">This second book in the series returns to the alternate world that Susan visited in the first book. In this one, we follow the new Restorer - the unlikely hero, Kieran - as he struggles to come to terms with the One's call on his life. We also watch Susan's teenage son grow and mature in the strange new world.<br /><br />Again, this story is told beautifully, and the characters are easy to relate to. Another really great read!</span>
